quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Vuga uti: “Ndikinze ku Mubungabunzi w’abantu bose;"
  114,2,"Umwami Mugabe w’abantu, Yikenuye;"
  114,3,"Imana Nyene gusengwa n’abantu, ata yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa atari Yo;"
  114,4,"Inkingire inabi ya shetani itera amazinda kenshi iyo umuntu agoswe, ikanyegera iyo aninahaje Imana Allah;"
  114,5,"Itera amazinda n’amakenga mu mitima y’abantu, ikabosha gukora ibibi no kureka ibitegetswe;"
  114,6,"Ikomoka mu bwoko bw’Amajini n’ubw’abantu”."
